movie_name: Bassie & Adriaan: Een Schat aan herinneringen
short_description: Bas and Aad van Toor have worked together for fifty years. First for 25 years as the acrobat duo The Crocksons and then for 25 years as clown Bassie and acrobat Adriaan. They traveled the world for their popular television series....
